{"id":1639611,"retrievedAt":"2026-02-22T11:40:39.417Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1639611,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Polish Film Chronicle 61/26A","overview":"A holiday report shot by cameramen of the Polish Film Chronicle or foreign Chronicles’ operators. The journey begins with a visit to Cuba, where the society benefits from the revolution. A report from India shows Poles who participate in the process of industrialization of this country, which is still full of contrasts. A look at Stockholm, where forecasts predict that sun will shine in three days. The farthest journey to Tokyo - basically it is a trip into the unknown and the city seems to be different than we have imagined. Cairo is much closer – the city is a unique blend of Arab tradition and modernity (with a view at pyramids) . We return to Europe via Italy. Even though we seem to know this country, it is still full of surprises.","popularity":0.05,"poster_path":"/8mXO5ZlN288kPfK5nhHwCt0YHVR.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":2466,"logo_path":"/596Eq7ivA0DpNfB5zzDU7yMeTB4.png","name":"Wytwórnia Filmów Dokumentalnych i Fabularnych","origin_country":"PL"}],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"1961-06-26","revenue":0,"runtime":10,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Polish Film Chronicle 61/26A","video":true,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":2238641,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Włodzimierz Kmicik","original_name":"Włodzimierz Kmicik","popularity":0.2783,"profile_path":null,"cast_id":3,"character":"Voice-Over","credit_id":"6999ca96894239cb9cb28555","order":0}],"crew":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":3999918,"known_for_department":"Sound","name":"Marek Lusztig","original_name":"Marek Lusztig","popularity":0.475,"profile_path":null,"credit_id":